  • Constructor Details

    • Invoice

      public Invoice​(String orderid, String orderDate, String orderTime, RRPSS.Staff s, List<order.OrderItems> itemList, double subTotalCost, double serviceCharge, double gst, double discount, double totalCost)
      Create Invoice with orderid,orderDate,orderTime,staff object,item list,subTotalCost,serviceCharge,gst,discount,totalCost
      Parameters:
      orderid - is the invoice id for this invoice.
      orderDate - is the order creation date in dd/MM/yyyy format.
      orderTime - is the order creation time in HH:mm format.
      s - is the reference of staff object that created the order.
      itemList - is the list of items that this invoice contains.
      subTotalCost - is the invoice cost before additional charges or discounts.
      serviceCharge - is the invoice service charge.
      gst - is the invoice GST charge.
      discount - is the invoice discount.
      totalCost - is the invoice total end cost.
